cs.LG, cs.RO, cs.AI, cs.CV, cs.SY

This paper involves model-based Reinforcement Learning (RL) for robot manipulation tasks using predictive models learned directly from vision and proprioception. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also involves robot manipulation tasks, which suggests the category cs.RO (Robotics). Additionally, the paper involves policy optimization, which suggests the category cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also involves learning from vision, which suggests the category cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper involves transfer learning, which suggests the category cs.SY (Systems and Control).
